query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('argparse',
'facebook-like',
'instance',
'jcombobox',
'laravel-5.5',
'libcurl',
'matlab-figure',
'mediawiki',
'multi-tenant',
'openshift',
'physics',
'puppet',
'rdd',
'session-variables',
'video-capture');
